description: Vejii Holdings Ltd., a digital marketplace, offers plant-based and living products of various brands in Canada and the United States. It provides products in the categories of grocery, protein and sports nutrition, personal care, vitamins and supplements, vegan wines, and baby and kid supplies through its shopvejii.com direct-to-consumer e-commerce marketplace. The company was incorporated in 2019 and is headquartered in Kelowna, Canada.
